      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">車鄰.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有車鄰鄰，有馬白顛。未見君子，寺人之令。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He has many carriages, giving forth their lin-lin.
He has horses with their white foreheads.
Before we can see our prince,
We must get the services of the eunuch.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qinfeng-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
