      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·001.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">車鄰.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>阪有漆，隰有栗。既見君子，並坐鼓瑟。今者不樂，逝者其耋。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hill-sides are varnish trees;
In the low wet grounds are chestnuts.
When we have seen our prince,
We sit together with him, and they play on their lutes.
If now we do not take our joy,
The time will pass till we are octogenarians.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
