      <prop type="x-translation-ref">車鄰.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>阪有桑，隰有楊。既見君子，並坐鼓簧。今者不樂，逝者其亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hill-sides are mulberry trees;
In the low wet grounds are willows.
When we have seen our prince,
We sit together with him, and they play on their organs.
If now we do not take our joy,
The time will pass till we are no more.</seg>
      </tuv>
